  "title": "Buying the Nice Chicken",
  "lessonText": "Choosing the right chicken is essential for a delicious curry.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Look for fresh, high-quality chicken.\n- Check for a pink color and firm texture.\n- Avoid chicken with any off smells.\n- Consider organic or free-range options for better flavor.\n- Buy from trusted sources or local markets."
  }
}
